2HourGame Readme (Alpha)

XNA Game Studio 3.1 + Visual Studio Express 2008 are required.


Players control ships with XBox 360 controllers.
Get as much gold from central island to your own.

Only player one can use keyboard.

Default Keys

Keyboard
Fire Left Cannons:	Space
Fire Right Cannons:	Space
Repair:			F
Load/Unload Gold:	F
Turn: Arrow Left or Arror Right
Forwared: Arrow Up


Game Pad
Fire Left Cannons: Left Trigger
Fire Right Cannons: Right Trigger
Repair:	(Check button icon)
Load/Unload Gold: (Check button icon)
Steering: Right Analog Stick
Forward: Right Analog Stick